Management strategies for heavily calcified coronary stenoses: an EAPCI clinical 
consensus statement in collaboration with the EURO4C-PCR group.

Barbato E(1), Gallinoro E(2), Abdel-Wahab M(3), Andreini D(2)(4), Carrié D(5), 
