Safety and efficacy of valbenazine for the treatment of chorea associated with 
Huntington's disease (KINECT-HD): a phase 3, randomised, double-blind, 
placebo-controlled trial.

Furr Stimming E(1), Claassen DO(2), Kayson E(3), Goldstein J(3), Mehanna R(4), 
Zhang H(5), Liang GS(5), Haubenberger D(5); Huntington Study Group KINECT-HD 
Collaborators.

