A nurse-led intervention in patients with newly diagnosed cancer and Type 2 
diabetes: A pilot randomized controlled trial feasibility study.

Scarton L(1), Nelson T(1), Jo A(2), O'Neal LJ(3), Yao Y(1), Huggins S(1), 
Legaspi AB(4), McClaren MJ(1), Cabassa JS(1), Burgos Melendez JM(1), Munoz-Pena 
JM(5), Markham MJ(6), Murphy MC(6), Chatzkel JA(6), Rogers S(6), George TJ(6).

Author information:
(1)College of Nursing, University of Florida, Gainesville, Florida, USA.
(2)College of Public Health and Health Professions, University of Florida, 
Gainesville, Florida, USA.
(3)College of Agricultural and Life Sciences, Institute of Food and Agricultural 
Sciences, University of Florida, Gainesville, Florida, USA.
(4)College of Pharmacy, University of Florida, Gainesville, Florida, USA.
(5)Division of Endocrinology, Diabetes and Metabolism, University of Florida 
